data.title: List of prima ballerinas
data.meta_description: This is a list of people who have been awarded the title prima ballerina, the second highest title that can be awarded to a ballerina: prima ballerina assoluta being the first.
data.text:
This is a list of people who have been awarded the title prima ballerina, the second highest title that can be awarded to a ballerina: prima ballerina assoluta being the first.

See also the categories Ballerinas and Male ballet dancers

See also: Prima ballerina assoluta
